--- layout: post title: Pacific Crest Trail Map --- This is a test of a leaflet map made in R, and ported over via jekyll to this post. It's a fairly simple map of the Pacific Crest Trail, which I hope to hike in it's entirety one day. Maybe not all at once, but certainly in segments. It's a truly amazing trail, I've done chunks of it, including the John Muir Trail and a decent stretch south of Ebbetts Pass.
